The purpose of this is to build an AI agent that will reccomend stocks, 

Some ideas:

Use OpenBB Terminal tor analyzing stocks, cryptocurrency. Can utilize machine learning for forecasting. Can also use finanical APIs. 
OpenBB

USe TensorTrade to build trading algorithms using reinforcement learning. Can simulate trading environments. Plays nice with TensorFlow and PyTorch. Train reinforcement learning models to recommend daily trades or stocks.

Use Alpaca AI Agent for stock trading via API.


Use Backtrader with Custom Models for backtesting trading strategies.

Use PyPortfolioOpt to optimize portfolio and FinRL (Financial Reinforcement Learning) 